Dependencies

The following is a list of dependencies for this project. These dependencies are required to compile and run the application:

Artifact ID Type Version URL Comment
ant jar 1.6.2 http://ant.apache.org/ Optional
jsch jar 0.1.23 http://www.jcraft.com/jsch/ Optional
commons-collections jar 3.1 http://jakarta.apache.org/commons/collections/ Optional
commons-httpclient jar 2.0.2 http://jakarta.apache.org/commons/httpclient/ Optional
commons-logging jar 1.0.4 http://jakarta.apache.org/commons/logging/
commons-net jar 1.4.1 http://jakarta.apache.org/commons/net/ Optional
jdom jar 1.0 http://www.jdom.org/ Optional
maven-xdoc-plugin plugin 1.9.2 http://maven.apache.org/reference/plugins/xdoc/ Site - Only required for building the website/documentation.
oro jar 2.0.8 http://jakarta.apache.org/oro/ Optional
xml-apis jar 1.0.b2 http://xml.apache.org/commons/ Optional
